<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Portfolio</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
</head>

<body>
  <header>
    <nav>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="#about">About</a></li>
        <li><a href="#portfolio">Portfolio</a></li>
        <li><a href="#contact">Contact</a></li>
      </ul>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <section id="about">
    <h2>About Me</h2>
    <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Nullam condimentum purus sit amet aliquet
      efficitur. Mauris auctor augue mi, ac eleifend nisl vestibulum in. Sed ut nibh vel ligula tempus volutpat
      vel at est. Sed a felis sed mi scelerisque iaculis non vitae ex. Curabitur gravida ex a tempus molestie.
      Fusce vel purus eu risus condimentum pulvinar sed a turpis. </p>
  </section>

  <section id="portfolio">
    <h2>Portfolio</h2>
    <div class="project">
      <img src="project1.jpg" alt="Project 1">
      <h3>Project 1</h3>
      <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="project">
      <img src="project2.jpg" alt="Project 2">
      <h3>Project 2</h3>
      <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="contact">
    <h2>Contact Me</h2>
    <form>
      <label for="name">Name:</label>
      <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required>
      <label for="email">Email:</label>
      <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required>
      <label for="message">Message:</label>
      <textarea id="message" name="message" required></textarea>
      <button type="submit">Send</button>
    </form>
  </section>

  <footer>
    <p>&copy; 2023 Your Name</p>
  </footer>
</body>

</html>
